  "title": "Central Kitchen Helper ( SALARY FROM $2180 /11AM-8PM / SUN OFF ）",
  "description": "<p>· Cutting vegetable, meat, poultry, fish and mince meat</p>\n<p>· Prepare sauces, spices, seasonings and marinades based on standard recipes</p>\n<p>· Preparation and production of soup (Bak Kut Teh, Tonkatsu Soup etc.)</p>\n<p>· Prepare gyoza ingredient, making gyoza &amp; gyoza skin (by machine)</p>\n<p>· Preparation and production of mochi</p>\n<p>· Receive and store food products at designated area</p>\n<p>· Packing of food and storage</p>\n<p>· Baking of tarts</p>\n<p>· Cleaning of equipment and tools and waste disposal</p>\n<p>· Handle any other duties assigned by Manager</p>\n<p>· Assist in back up noodle, bakery and packing department if needed</p>\n<p>· Follow company safety SOP and wear safety equipment while working in the kitchen</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· 切蔬菜、肉类、鸡、鱼类和绞肉</p>\n<p>· 根据标准食谱准备酱料、香料、调味料和腌汁</p>\n<p>· 准备汤料和烹煮（肉骨茶、猪骨汤等）</p>\n<p>· 准备饺子馅料，包饺子和做饺子皮 (机器制作)</p>\n<p>· 接收并存储食物在指定的储存区</p>\n<p>· 食品包装和储存</p>\n<p>· 清洗厨房设备、用具和倒垃圾</p>\n<p>· 处理主管分配的其他工作</p>\n<p>· 遵从公司的安全准则，在厨房工作是佩戴安全设备</p>",
